      <bioghist id="aspace_dabde77080af79bc83b53db0e36cba8b">
         <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
         <p>The Yale University Office of Public Affairs, formerly the News Bureau and the Office of Public Information, publishes and distributes press releases, announcements, promotional films, and the Yale Bulletin and Calendar.</p>  
      </bioghist>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_223f78936c7fc07e7ea6cdb223064c25">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of correspondence and program and administrative files of the Yale Office of Public Affairs. Included are records documenting the Yale Reports and the correspondence of Walter D. Littell, director.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
