            <scopecontent id="aspace_2f2bb9461f140daec3369b40242ccb52">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The records consist primarily of material on the <emph render="italic">Yale Reports,</emph>a series of radio programs which featured Yale professors discussing contemporary issues, from 1958-1972 and correspondence 1951-1972. The correspondence documents the day to day operations and activities of the department.</p>
